@CodingTestApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Get all products (V1)
GET {{CodingTestApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all products (V2 - Enhanced Response)
GET {{CodingTestApi_HostAddress}}/api/v2/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Get product by ID (V1)
GET {{CodingTestApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get product by ID (V2)
GET {{CodingTestApi_HostAddress}}/api/v2/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new product (V1)
POST {{CodingTestApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Monitor",
  "price": 299.99,
  "description": "4K Ultra HD Monitor"
}

###

### Create a new product (V2 - with enhanced validation)
POST {{CodingTestApi_HostAddress}}/api/v2/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Headphones",
  "price": 149.99,
  "description": "Wireless noise-cancelling headphones"
}

###

### Get application info (Configuration from appsettings.json)
GET {{CodingTestApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/configuration/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all configuration settings (Demonstrates reading from appsettings.json)
GET {{CodingTestApi_HostAddress}}/api/v1/configuration/settings
Accept: application/json

###

